{"tid":1428670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心「求救」，慎防舉證撚","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:50:54.000Z","uid":77872,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16d207e18c46cbf6f247f2c786b74a66fde5e617","tid":1428670,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"近排陰啲陰啲見到有啲post<br />\n「求救！手足比人拉咗！求相同片」類型嘅post，叫你send啲source去某個電話，係某個律師團體<br />\n<br />\n喺度提醒咁多位，有心幫人係好事，但係要諗真啲。<br />\n第一，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係普通法下，舉證係控方責任證明有罪，唔會要求辯方搵證據證明自己無罪。</span></span><br />\n第二，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「轉發」嘅post</span></span>，點解唔知直接講係咩團體，你都放得個電話number出嚟，怕咩比人知。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅出發點係提大家行事小心，因為有可能有狗混入人群，你send咗當時啲片/相去，比popo攞到，分分鐘會入你數charge你當時在場，到時就gg<br />\n<br />\n點都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"47b77ab5b5571c5b97a0a53f5718a211e6bc19ee","tid":1428670,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"483b367240c59e1c19ad36918e13dcb7604094b7","tid":1428670,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"985068bda916da2f631ed4cf7af4a97cf867486e","tid":1428670,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br /